        "subject": "LU-19749 ldiskfs: remove 4.12-sles15sp1 ldiskfs series",
        "message": "LU-19749 ldiskfs: remove 4.12-sles15sp1 ldiskfs series\n\nThe 4.12-sles15sp1 and earlier kernels are no longer supported.\n\nRemove the ldiskfs-4.12-sles15*.series file and all patches that\nare no longer used by this (or other) patch series.\n\nRunning \"./contrib/scripts/clearpatches.sh ldiskfs/kernel_patches\"\nwill report which patches are no longer used by any series file.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I6f1a7348aba1764eaec59ef3a74b88b51a3ebbe5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64108\nReviewed-by: Minh <mdiep@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
